<main class="detail-shell">
  <section class="detail-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">RLS Protected Access</p>
    <h1>Access requires a Slack-issued one-time link</h1>
    <p class="hero-copy">
      This directory is restricted to verified RLS members. In Slack, run
